<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>LeetCode Report Generator</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #0f172a;
      color: #f1f5f9;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100vh;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .banner {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #facc15;
      color: #0f172a;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-align: center;
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .banner a {
      color: #0f172a;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .container {
      background-color: #1e293b;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 100px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #facc15;
    }

    form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    input[type="text"],
    input[type="date"],
    select {
      padding: 12px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      border: 1px solid #334155;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background-color: #0f172a;
      color: #f8fafc;
      font-size: 1rem;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }

    input:focus,
    select:focus {
      border-color: #facc15;
    }

    label {
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }

    button {
      margin-top: 25px;
      padding: 12px;
      background-color: rgb(44, 187, 93);
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: rgb(36, 160, 80);
    }

    .dev-note {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #facc15;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: auto;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 16px 0;
      background-color: #1e293b;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #facc15;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="banner">
    ‚ö†Ô∏è Prerequisite: Your repository must follow the <strong>LeetSync</strong> structure. For reference, check the <a href="https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/leetsync-leetcode-to-gith/ppkbejeolfcbaomanmbpjdbkfcjfhjnd?hl=en" target="_blank">live example</a>.
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>Daily LeetCode Report</h1>
    <form action="/submit" method="POST">
      <input type="text" name="githubUser" placeholder="GitHub Username" required>
      <input type="text" name="repoName" placeholder="Repo Name" required>

      <label for="language">Choose a programming language:</label>
      <select name="language" id="language" required>
        <option value=".cpp">C++ (.cpp)</option>
        <option value=".c">C (.c)</option>
        <option value=".java">Java (.java)</option>
        <option value=".py">Python (.py)</option>
        <option value=".js">JavaScript (.js)</option>
        <option value=".ts">TypeScript (.ts)</option>
        <option value=".rb">Ruby (.rb)</option>
        <option value=".go">Go (.go)</option>
        <option value=".rs">Rust (.rs)</option>
        <option value=".swift">Swift (.swift)</option>
        <option value=".kt">Kotlin (.kt)</option>
        <option value=".php">PHP (.php)</option>
        <option value=".cs">C# (.cs)</option>
        <option value=".html">HTML (.html)</option>
        <option value=".css">CSS (.css)</option>
        <option value=".sh">Shell Script (.sh)</option>
        <option value=".sql">SQL (.sql)</option>
        <option value=".r">R (.r)</option>
        <option value=".dart">Dart (.dart)</option>
        <option value=".scala">Scala (.scala)</option>
      </select>

      <label for="fromDate">From Date:</label>
      <input type="date" id="fromDate" name="fromDate" required>

      <label for="toDate">To Date:</label>
      <input type="date" id="toDate" name="toDate" required>

      <button type="submit">Generate Report</button>
    </form>

    <div class="dev-note">
      üöß This tool is still under development. New features are on the way!
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    Made with ‚ù§Ô∏è by
    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/anuragpandey0711/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a> |
    <a href="https://github.com/pandeyji711" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
